*textutils-2.0.21 (26 Aug 2002)

  26 Aug 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> textutils-2.0.21.ebuild
  files/digest-textutils-2.0.21 :

  rossm@nist.gov (Ross J. Micheals) in bug #6842 reports that od gives
  incorrect output in the 2.0.19 version.  This release fixes that problem.

*textutils-2.0.19-r1 (21 Jul 2002)

  21 Jul 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :
  Move /usr/bin/wc to /bin/wc for upcomming baselayout.

