  Added LICENSE, KEYWORDS, SLOT.

  18 Mar 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> textutils-2.0.19-r1 :

  The patch in ${FILESDIR} is to remove RMS's rant about fascism and the
